data.description: Welcome Home! Amazing move-in ready 3-bedroom, 2-bath ranch on a full partially finished basement!! New Year, Newer construction. Home built in 2020. Situated in the middle of the culdesac, the lot sits on .48 acres, with a small stream out back! A perfect blend of contemporary/modern features. Open concept. The kitchen features, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, cabinets with close-touch  features, and an open view into the great  room. Gorgeous eat-in kitchen area with a  bay window. Home barely lived in, offers a  large master on the main with tray ceilings,  a separate elegant garden tub, a separate  glass shower and toilet room, a walk-in  closet, and a double vanity. Two separate  secondary bedrooms on the other side of  the home offering a full bathroom. Plush  carpet and neutral-color laminate flooring  throughout. Temporal rec room in the  basement along with a massive space for  additional entertainment. Basement has a  separate entrance and fully operable  window. NO HOA!!! Go see this beauty  today and let's make a deal! All offers will  be viewed by January 31, 2024. Owner  /Agent has a vested interested in the sale  of the home. Combo lockbox - Showingtime
